# 8004-atom checkout. This makes `cargo build` / `anchor build` use your
# local ATOM source instead of fetching from GitHub.
#
# .cargo/config.toml is gitignored â€” your local path stays private.
#
# Usage:
#   cp .cargo/config.toml.example .cargo/config.toml
